3.3 Goal

In this project, students will be required to create a web application using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. They will also need to understand and use Markdown to format their project‚Äôs documentation. Additionally, they will need to use GitHub and Visual Code to manage their project‚Äôs code and collaborate with their peers.


