Create a HouseDirector class that controls the building process using the ConcreteHouseBuilder class:

public class HouseDirector {
    private ConcreteHouseBuilder builder;

    public HouseDirector() {
        this.builder = new ConcreteHouseBuilder();
    }

    public void buildHouse() {
        builder.buildWalls();
        builder.buildRoof();
        builder.buildDoors();
    }
    public House getHouse(){
        return builder.getHouse();
    }
}

In the main method, we can create an instance of the HouseDirector, and use the Director to build the house:

    public static void main(String[] args) {
